node.text: In case you haven’t heard, I own part of a company called Filtertime. We mail you air filters for your home HVAC on subscription. We launched a new product just recently. Air Filters for RV owners. I didn’t even know this was a thing and I’ve been using RVs my entire adult life. I wish I’d known about this years ago. Check us out at Filtertime.com for your air filter needs.
